				I've occasionally had this problem, though not I think intentionally.  I don't interrupt the spell, if it aggroes me I kill it, if it aggroes them I right off the lost mana and let them have it. <br>  <br> If you think they're doing it on purpose (ie if it happens more than once) then I would suggest switching to your level one shock, it's casting time should beat them getting there and clear up the issue of who's kill stealing.  Of course neither of you will look good in this situation, so it may just be better to move on. <br>  <br> 		

